    return df, ax

df = pd.read_csv(csv_file)
    df.replace({'dict_column': '{"key": "value"}'}, {"dict_column": '{"key": "value"}'}, regex=True, inplace=True)

    df.dropna(inplace=True)
    df.dict_column = df.dict_column.apply(str)
    pair_grid = sns.PairGrid(df, hue='hue_value', vars=['column_1', 'column_2', 'column_3', 'column_4'], palette='vlag')

    ax.add_legend(ncol=4)
    return df, ax
